  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. The model predicts absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed across all 13 credibility factors. Seven factors are formally assessed; six are flagged as epistemic gaps. All assessed factors meet or exceed the required gradation for MRL 5. Decision: Accepted under the Minimal-profile submission pathway. Intended use scope — absolute hemolysis index prediction for pre-market regulatory submission of a centrifugal VAD operating at 3–6 L/min flow and 2000–4500 rpm — is described in the bound Claim and Requirement nodes; no structured hasContextOfUse object is linked.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-vad-hemolysis-mrl5",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cfd-hemolysis-class3-vad",
