      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite achieving gradation 4; all regression tests pass.",
      "rationale": "OpenFOAM v9 is under full version control with a 1,200-case regression suite. All tests pass. Independent code review completed. Gradation 4 achieved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to governing equations with demonstrated order-of-accuracy convergence.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to the Navier-Stokes and power-law hemolysis transport equations. Second-order spatial convergence confirmed on three systematically refined meshes."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation-based GCI reported for all primary QoIs; GCI < 2% on fine mesh.",
      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation performed on three meshes (3.2M, 9.8M, 28.4M cells). GCI on hemolysis index is 1.4% on the fine mesh. Gradation 4 satisfied."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
