      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs directly map to decision-relevant clinical endpoints; traceability documented.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index (normalized index of hemolysis, NIH) is the primary regulatory endpoint for VAD blood-contacting devices. Traceability from model output to clinical endpoint is documented in the bound Requirement node."
