      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted at operating conditions bracketing the intended VAD use envelope.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments span 2.5–6.5 L/min and 1800–4800 rpm, fully bracketing the intended 3–6 L/min, 2000–4500 rpm VAD operating envelope stated in the bound Claim."
    },
