      "acceptanceCriteria": "Monte Carlo or equivalent UQ propagating all material and boundary-condition uncertainties through the model to QoI uncertainty bounds.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo sampling framework is implemented but only three of eleven uncertain input parameters have been propagated. Full input UQ is incomplete at MRL 5 requirements."
