      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal mapping between validation experiment input parameters and COU input parameters with documented equivalency argument.",
      "rationale": "Bovine blood used in validation experiments; human blood properties assumed in COU model. Species-equivalency argument for rheological parameters has not been formally documented. Epistemic gap."
